Class User

java.lang.Object
User
Direct Known Subclasses:
Customer, Host
public abstract class User extends Object
An abstract class representing a user with basic information such as user ID, date of birth, first name, last name, and registration date. This class provides constructors for creating instances with different sets of information and getter and setter methods for accessing and modifying the user's attributes.
Version:
1.0
Author:
Mert Can Bilgin
